    <p>The industrial building of <strong>Radialsystem V</strong> creates the perfect setting for a great day: located in the heart of Berlin, right next to the river Spree, our venue is very close to hotels, nightlife, restaurants and the buzzing Mitte, Kreuzberg and Friedrichshain districts.</p>

    <p>The distance from your hotel to the venue is <a href="https://www.google.de/maps/dir/Ibis+am+Ostbahnhof,+An+der+Schillingbr%C3%BCcke+2,+10243+Berlin/Radialsystem+V,+Holzmarktstra%C3%9Fe+33,+10243+Berlin/@52.5102384,13.4272308,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m13!4m12!1m5!1m1!1s0x47a84e38597caced:0x19ac055ffedc41b!2m2!1d13.429641!2d52.509875!1m5!1m1!1s0x47a84e3900263f87:0xf3893f5141a5c0fc!2m2!1d13.428635!2d52.510387?hl=en" target="_blank">just 140m</a>.</p>

